--- project detail page: add issues+PRs panel ---

TARGET FILE: /home/jkh/.rcc/workspace/rcc/api/index.mjs
FUNCTION: projectDetailHtml() — the function that generates the HTML string returned for GET /projects/:id

=== STEP 1: Add CSS ===
In the <style> block, after the line containing `.status-failed{...}`, add:

    .gh-panel{margin-top:1rem}
